title: [Apple Orchard, Scorched]
description: The south-facing sides of the trees here are dotted with burns and singed spots.  Despite the damage, their limbs are laden with ripe fruit, and a small barn owl circles overhead, seeking a juicy target.
The south-facing sides of the trees here are dotted with burns and singed spots.  Despite the damage, their limbs are laden with ripe fruit, and a blue jay circles overhead, seeking a juicy target.
